children.label: "SELECT g.id, g.species_id, ps.value FROM genes AS g INNER JOIN gene_refs AS gr USING (id) INNER JOIN genes2proteins AS g2p ON (g.id = g2p.gene_id) INNER JOIN protein_strings AS ps ON (g2p.protein_id = ps.id) WHERE g.species_id IN (9606, 10090, 10116) AND ps.cat = 'symbol' AND gr.accesion IN "

"UNION SELECT g.id, g.species_id, gs.value FROM genes AS g INNER JOIN gene_refs AS gr USING (id) INNER JOIN gene_strings AS gs USING (id) WHERE gs.cat = 'symbol' AND g.species_id IN (9606, 10090, 10116) "
